12:27.789 --> 12:29.708
we saved you
the inflatable unicorn.

12:29.708 --> 12:32.294
Well, thank you.

12:32.294 --> 12:33.712
- You want some?
- Yeah.
- [Belly] Very cute.

12:33.712 --> 12:35.005
Hey, guys.

12:35.005 --> 12:37.007
Hey. Check out who I found.

12:37.007 --> 12:38.383
- It's Cam Cameron.
- [all] Cam!

12:38.383 --> 12:40.010
Oh, I'm good, man.
Thank you, I don't drink.

12:40.010 --> 12:41.595
Yes, that's right. More for me.

12:41.595 --> 12:42.971
That's fine.

12:42.971 --> 12:44.556
- Cool...
- Hey, soul buddy.

12:44.556 --> 12:46.308
- Hey, Jere.
- Hey, Shayla.

12:46.308 --> 12:48.226
- What's up, Gigi?
- [Cam] Hi, there.
- [Belly] Hi.

12:48.226 --> 12:49.728
- What's up?
- Um...

12:49.728 --> 12:51.855
- What is that?
- It's...

12:51.855 --> 12:53.356
a pomegranate margarita.

12:54.941 --> 12:56.359
It's not a race, Con.

12:56.359 --> 12:57.944
Yeah, save some
for the rest of us, please.

12:57.944 --> 12:59.571
[laughs]

12:59.571 --> 13:02.157
[Belly] Okay, wait, wait, wait.
But what if it was a race?

13:02.157 --> 13:04.034
I mean, isn't that... isn't...

13:04.034 --> 13:06.828
Isn't that the premise
of, like, every drinking game?

13:06.828 --> 13:10.290
You want to play
a drinking game?

13:10.290 --> 13:12.751
Why not? I mean,
it's the Fourth of July, right?

13:12.751 --> 13:14.252
- Fuck it.
- Let's do it.

13:14.252 --> 13:16.296
[all cheer]

13:16.296 --> 13:17.297
[Jeremiah] Oh, I got it!

13:17.297 --> 13:18.465
Drink!

13:18.465 --> 13:20.050
[laughter]

13:20.050 --> 13:22.385
